vooga.towerdefense.attributes

Class AttributeManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • vooga.towerdefense.attributes.AttributeManager
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    DefaultAttributeManager

    public class AttributeManager
extends Object
    Attributes object that helps to track all game element stats. It also provides info requested by view through controller. Used by Towers, Units, Weapons and any Asset-based object.
    Author:
    Matthew Roy, XuRui, Zhen Gou
